/* Function: iqrf.embed.coordinator.EnableRemoteBonding_Request
Encodes DPA request to enable remote bonding.

Parameters:
  bondingMask - number: see DPA technical documentation.
  control - number: see DPA technical documentation.
  userData - array: Array of 4 bytes, see DPA technical documentation.

Returns:
  string: DPA request string.
*/
